explanations.description: Truncated or modified words, often missing a prefix, such as "coinc-" instead of "coincidence", or "chartered" being split into "char-" and "tered", with the missing part being implied in the context, or words with suffixes and prefixes like "spacecraft", "midwife" and " midwives".
